                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "March 7, 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Upon receiving a message from the ancient lamp out of the blue, even the Great Adventurer of the Realms, Dodo-King, Defender of Old Mondstadt, Author of the Teyvat Travel Guide, Elder of the Hexenzirkel, Codename \"A,\" Mother of the Most Adorable Klee — Alice was taken aback.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Fortunately, it was not a disastrous incident that had prompted the message. Instead, it served to bring back memories of companions whom she shared her youth with.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
